data.description: New construction to be complete Summer 2021, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Twin Oaks, blends small town charm with big city conveniences!. located just West of the City of Lowell in the Lowell School District. The downtown area of Lowell features a unique shopping & dining district and wonderful artistic environment to explore. RESNET ENERGY SMART NEW CONSTRUCTION-10 YEAR STRUCTURAL WARRANTY. Welcome home to over 2,000 square feet of living space on 2 levels. The foyer welcomes and leads into a large great room, open to the gorgeous kitchen, featuring a center island with pendant lighting, granite counters, tile backsplash and spacious dining nook. The large mud room is a multi-functional space, tucked away from the main living space, and includes a walk-in laundry room as well as a powder room. Upstairs find the large master suite complete with WIC and private full bath. 3 more spacious bedrooms and another full bath complete this home. Walkout basement has good natural light.
